@startuml
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
[*] --> Draft
Draft --> Closed : confirm
Closed --> Pending : process
Pending --> OnHold : update
Pending : entry / log post
OnHold --> Approved : review
Approved --> Rejected : review
Approved : entry / log post
Approved --> OnHold : revert
Rejected --> [*]
@enduml